author: @chiizuzu
text:
Cast:

Kun: Reminds the team to look at the big picture when they're stuck. 9:38 Very supportive of the members' ideas - even if they don't seem like the right answer. 26:43
Renjun: Takes initiative to solve and completes many of the riddles, but very easily (and adorably) startled. 24:00
Jeno: Ready to try anything - most of it by force. "Should we just crush it?" 3:00 "Should we take the gown off?" 19:50
Jaemin: At first, seems like he's trying a bit, but then slowly loses his mind. 27:21 Also, acts as a safety wall for Renjun. 11:09
Shotaro: Certified Japanese translator. 4:22 Tries his best to help, but mostly at dead ends with the hints. Still very cute though! 10/10 efforts were made. 25:22
Sungchan: Not scared. Mostly here to have fun and mess around. Scares Renjun in the process.17:57 Tries to mess with the actor, too. 12:09 Not all his pranks work, but he's still very excited about them. 15:53
Chenle: Not scared. Mostly here to have fun and mess around. Scares Renjun in the process. (2) 21:12 Not very good as ASMR, but at least he is very polite about it. 14:43
